# 📖 Project Overview

This project demonstrates the deployment of a full-stack e-commerce application on AWS following a 3-tier architecture.

The application consists of:

- React Frontend
- Spring Boot REST API
- MySQL Database
- AWS Cloud Infrastructure

The frontend is hosted on Amazon S3 and delivered globally through Amazon CloudFront. The backend runs on an EC2 instance inside a custom VPC, while the database is hosted on Amazon RDS.

---

# 🏗 Architecture

```
                     User
                       │
                       ▼
                CloudFront CDN
                       │
                       ▼
            Amazon S3 (React App)
                       │
               HTTPS API Calls
                       ▼
          Amazon EC2 (Spring Boot)
                       │
                JDBC Connection
                       ▼
            Amazon RDS (MySQL)
```

